title: Sialathin

properties.name: description
properties.value: Sialathin was a citizen originally from a settlement in Hallowvale. He wrote the dusty scroll, a letter to his girlfriend, Lantania, in which he promises that he will find her and bring them across the River Salve.

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Sialathin

Sialathin was a citizen originally from a settlement in Hallowvale. He wrote the dusty scroll, a letter to his girlfriend, Lantania, in which he promises that he will find her and bring them across the River Salve.
